      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LADY ROSALYN (1) comes off an average effort last start when sixth at this track over 400m behind Extravagantly (24.10) in a TG1-4W. Scored at her previous run. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Has ability and can bounce back. MIRACLE MAN (8) has mixed form recently, finishing sixth (22.96) in a T3 RSTW at Ballarat latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Can find the frame this time. LEKTRA LEE (6) ran good time (23.17) winning a TG1-4W three back at this track but missed the frame latest finishing sixth at this track. Solid beginner and with a good start can clear the tricky draw. Has the ability and expected to do much better. CADILLAC CLASS (4) is right in the mix.",
